The data collection tool of my choice is Google Form and
the tool is address to the local health care professionals and practitionners affiliated and having access to patients data records;
Here is the link for the review https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdtYsZoRxaGZe2quYLOMRc9KOmQIc-dwiyFPH2Dng1qu859DA/viewform?usp=pp_url

The offline solution I could think of and suggest is a mobile app, Teamscope app.
Teamscope app is offline android and iOS mobile survey app specifically designed for sensitive and clinical data collection research. It collect qualitative and quantitative data offline.
Data collected are also encrypted.
